data.description:
This delightful 4-bedroom, 1-bathroom home is the perfect setting for creating lasting memories with family and friends. Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, this property offers a  an inviting inground pool that's sure to be the centerpiece of your summer gatherings. What's more, this home is fully powered by municipal electric, including heating, ensuring both efficiency and comfort.
Don't miss your chance to make this charming house your forever home, just in time to host unforgettable holiday gatherings. Contact us today to schedule a showing and experience the warmth and comfort this property has to offer!
